<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:09:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京访问朝鲜时金正恩誓言支持俄罗斯在乌克兰的军事行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kim-jong-un-vows-support-for-russias-military-actions-in-ukraine-as-putin-visits-north-korea/articleshow/111109816.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111109816.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 09:35:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kim-jong-un-vows-support-for-russias-military-actions-in-ukraine-as-putin-visits-north-korea/articleshow/111109816.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着俄罗斯和朝鲜加深关系，中国保持距离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-keeps-its-distance-as-russia-and-north-korea-deepen-ties/articleshow/111107487.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111107487.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国谨慎地关注朝鲜和俄罗斯加强关系，警惕使中国与其他国家的关系复杂化。北京避免与莫斯科和平壤结成三边联盟，担心朝鲜与俄罗斯的军事合作及其对地区稳定和自身地缘政治影响的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-keeps-its-distance-as-russia-and-north-korea-deepen-ties/articleshow/111107487.cms</guid></item><item><title>希腊外长表示欧洲必须收容受战争影响的加沙儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-must-host-gaza-children-impacted-by-war-greek-foreign-minister-says/articleshow/111107554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111107554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;希腊外长乔治·杰拉佩特里蒂斯以人道主义理由为由，主张欧洲暂时收容受加沙冲突影响的儿童。尽管移民问题存在政治敏感性，当选为联合国安理会成员的希腊仍寻求促进这一努力。杰拉佩特里蒂斯强调，这一倡议是人道主​​义的，与移民无关，旨在解决加沙因战争和饥荒而加剧的严重人道主义危机。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:04:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-must-host-gaza-children-impacted-by-war-greek-foreign-minister-says/articleshow/111107554.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国遭受暴雨袭击，山体滑坡造成九人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/landslides-kill-nine-as-bangladesh-lashed-by-rain/articleshow/111107158.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111107158.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国的暴雨引发山体滑坡，造成至少九人死亡、数千人流离失所。超过一百万人被困，学校被改造成避难所。锡尔赫特和苏南甘杰地区受到严重影响。气候变化正在加剧这个地势低洼、灾害频发的国家的季风影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:47:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/landslides-kill-nine-as-bangladesh-lashed-by-rain/articleshow/111107158.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京罕见访问老盟友朝鲜，旨在在美国制裁之际加强关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putins-rare-visit-to-old-ally-north-korea-aims-to-strengthen-ties-amid-us-sanctions/articleshow/111100332.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111100332.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京访问朝鲜，在美国主导的制裁下加强与金正恩的关系。普京抵达平壤机场后受到朝鲜领导人金正恩的热烈欢迎。两国领导人握手拥抱，金正恩亲自护送普京前往锦绣山国宾馆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:45:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putins-rare-visit-to-old-ally-north-korea-aims-to-strengthen-ties-amid-us-sanctions/articleshow/111100332.cms</guid></item><item><title>报道称，美国国会两位关键民主党人批准向以色列出售大规模武器</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-key-democrats-in-us-congress-approve-major-arms-sale-to-israel-reports/articleshow/111094604.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094604.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在拜登政府的压力下，美国国会两位有影响力的民主党人格雷戈里·米克斯和本·卡丁同意支持向以色列出售大量武器，其中包括价值超过 180 亿美元的 50 架 F-15 战斗机。该协议凸显了拜登总统在处理以色列-加沙冲突方面面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 22:08:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-key-democrats-in-us-congress-approve-major-arms-sale-to-israel-reports/articleshow/111094604.cms</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔因非正常移民增加而停止对中国公民免签</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ecuador-stops-waiving-visas-for-chinese-nationals-over-rise-in-irregular-migration/articleshow/111094634.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094634.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于移民流动异常，厄瓜多尔外交部恢复了对中国游客的签证要求。对逾期居留和滥用厄瓜多尔作为过境点的担忧导致了这一决定，强调了人口走私和缺乏离境登记等问题。该部的行动旨在加强边境管制并解决游客数量的差异。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 22:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ecuador-stops-waiving-visas-for-chinese-nationals-over-rise-in-irregular-migration/articleshow/111094634.cms</guid></item><item><title>比比指责美国扣留武器，减缓了以色列的行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibi-blames-us-for-withholding-weapons-slowing-israel-action/articleshow/111094605.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094605.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列总理内塔尼亚胡指责美国扣留武器，影响了加沙南部拉法的军事行动。冲突加剧了巴勒斯坦人的人道主义危机。出于对平民伤亡的担忧，拜登总统自五月以来推迟了重型炸弹的投送。内塔尼亚胡批评拜登，敦促采取工具来加快完成工作。安东尼·布林肯 (Antony Blinken) 谈到了在拉法等人口稠密地区使用 2000 磅炸弹的担忧，目前仍在审查中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 22:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bibi-blames-us-for-withholding-weapons-slowing-israel-action/articleshow/111094605.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京誓言支持朝鲜对抗美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-vows-to-support-north-korea-against-the-united-states/articleshow/111094571.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094571.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 在 24 年来首次访问朝鲜期间宣布了加强与朝鲜贸易和安全关系的计划。这次访问引发了人们对普京对朝鲜领导人金正恩的支持的担忧，因为美国正在审查俄罗斯支持朝鲜抵抗经济压力的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 22:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-vows-to-support-north-korea-against-the-united-states/articleshow/111094571.cms</guid></item><item><title>即将离任的荷兰首相马克·吕特是北约首席职位的最强候选人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/outgoing-dutch-pm-mark-rutte-strongest-nominee-for-nato-chief-post/articleshow/111094555.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094555.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/outgoing-dutch-pm-mark-rutte-strongest-nominee-for-nato-chief-post/articleshow/111094555.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰国通过同性婚姻法案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-passes-same-sex-marriage-bill/articleshow/111094523.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094523.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;泰国立法者批准了一项婚姻平等法案，正在等待参议院委员会、宪法法院的审查和皇室的同意。该立法将婚姻定义为两个年满 18 岁或以上的人之间的伙伴关系，为 LGBTQ 夫妇提供平等权利和公众对同性婚姻合法化的大力支持。该法案标志着泰国同性婚姻合法化迈出了重要一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-passes-same-sex-marriage-bill/articleshow/111094523.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约和美国希望中国为支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争付出代价</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-and-us-want-china-to-pay-for-propping-up-russias-ukraine-war/articleshow/111094521.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094521.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格和美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯对中国在乌克兰冲突中支持俄罗斯表示担忧，敦促采取报复措施。国家主席习近平、安东尼·布林肯和林健是紧张局势升级的关键人物。七国集团外长还对中国企业向俄罗斯转运物资表示强烈关切。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-and-us-want-china-to-pay-for-propping-up-russias-ukraine-war/articleshow/111094521.cms</guid></item><item><title>马萨诸塞州 911 发生重大故障，人们被要求拨打非紧急电话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/major-911-outage-in-massachusetts-people-asked-to-call-non-emergency-numbers/articleshow/111093747.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111093747.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; CNN 报道称，居民的手机收到公共安全警报信息，称全州 911 服务中断，公共安全响应可能会出现延误。 “如果您或其他人遇到紧急情况，请直接拨打当地公共安全业务热线。更多信息将在可用时提供。”警报中写道。目前尚不清楚导致 911 故障的原因。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/major-911-outage-in-massachusetts-people-asked-to-call-non-emergency-numbers/articleshow/111093747.cms</guid></item><item><title>梅根·马克尔和哈里王子被告知如果他们想受到欢迎就停止这种行为</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markle-prince-harry-told-to-stop-this-if-they-want-to-be-welcomed-back/articleshow/111094117.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111094117.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;王室表示，即使没有哈里和梅根，王室也非常团结。如果他们想被欢迎回到王室，他们就必须停止通过出售王室细节来赚钱。据王室专家称，哈里想家，因为梅根一直专注于她的好莱坞事业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:02:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markle-prince-harry-told-to-stop-this-if-they-want-to-be-welcomed-back/articleshow/111094117.cms</guid></item><item><title>贾斯汀·汀布莱克（Justin Timberlake）的眼睛呆滞，警察没有认出他：详细信息</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/justin-timberlake-had-glassy-eyes-cops-did-not-recognize-him-details/articleshow/111092885.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111092885.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;报道称，这位 43 岁的流行歌手被拘留，并被指控一项醉酒驾驶罪和另外两项交通违规罪：没有在停车标志处停车以及未能保持在正确的行驶车道上。拦下汀布莱克的警察太年轻了，他甚至不认识这位十届格莱美奖得主。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/justin-timberlake-had-glassy-eyes-cops-did-not-recognize-him-details/articleshow/111092885.cms</guid></item><item><title>凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 穿着旧裙子参加阅兵仪式，因为……</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-wore-old-dress-to-trooping-the-colour-because-/articleshow/111091542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111091542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 在健康问题和岳父查尔斯国王 (King Charles) 癌症治疗期间穿着一件旧连衣裙参加了皇家阅兵仪式，以绝密方式重返王室职责。只有少数人知道凯特的外表，其中之一是查尔斯国王，他很高兴凯特能参加皇室活动。专家观察到，今年凯特被安排在女王身边，两人的病情更加接近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:59:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-wore-old-dress-to-trooping-the-colour-because-/articleshow/111091542.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国歌手贾斯汀·汀布莱克因酒后驾车在纽约被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-singer-justin-timberlake-arrested-for-drink-driving-in-new-york/articleshow/111090192.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111090192.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-singer-justin-timberlake-arrested-for-drink-driving-in-new-york/articleshow/111090192.cms</guid></item><item><title>波音公司首席执行官在新指控中承认公司文化远非完美</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeings-culture-far-from-perfect-admits-ceo-amid-fresh-allegations/articleshow/111090776.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111090776.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名现任员工表示，波音公司向监管机构隐瞒了损坏或不合规格的零件，这些零件后来从未被追踪到，最终可能被安装在一些飞机上。面对参议院对正在进行的安全听证会的质询，波音公司首席执行官戴夫·卡尔霍恩承认，波音公司的文化远非完美。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:02:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/boeings-culture-far-from-perfect-admits-ceo-amid-fresh-allegations/articleshow/111090776.cms</guid></item><item><title>梅琳达与比尔盖茨离婚后：“这真是太棒了”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/melinda-after-divorcing-bill-gates-it-has-been-wonderful/articleshow/111089600.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111089600.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;梅琳达·弗伦奇在与比尔·盖茨离婚后过着充实的生活。在接受《时代》杂志采访时，她说她喜欢住在一个可以步行去小商店、药店或餐馆的社区。结婚27年后，盖茨夫妇于2021年5月宣布离婚。今年5月，梅琳达宣布辞去比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会联合主席职务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 13:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/melinda-after-divorcing-bill-gates-it-has-been-wonderful/articleshow/111089600.cms</guid></item><item><title>2024 年 6 月，哪些店开门营业，哪些店关门：Target、沃尔玛、星巴克</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/whats-open-and-whats-closed-on-juneteenth-2024-target-walmart-starbucks/articleshow/111090042.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111090042.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2024 年 6 月节假期：2024 年 6 月节假期，股市将于 6 月 19 日（星期三）休市，银行和邮局也将休市，但主要餐馆、杂货店和零售连锁店将在这个联邦假期正常营业，这是美国第二个假期独立日。据《今日美国》报道，塔吉特、沃尔玛、星巴克、好市多将继续营业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:28:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/whats-open-and-whats-closed-on-juneteenth-2024-target-walmart-starbucks/articleshow/111090042.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>